  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink284-kilavi">tiṉaiyarintuḻik kiḷiyai nōkkik kūṟuvāḷ pōl ciṟaippuṟamāka ōmpaṭuttatu. </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> What the hero, having fixed the time for marriage and parted, and then returning, said.          
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink284">
<l>aḷiya tāmē cevvāyp paiṅkiḷi</l>
<l>kuṉṟak kuṟavar koytiṉaip paiṅkā</l>
<l>liruvi nīḷpuṉaṅ kaṇṭum</l>
<l>pirita ṟēṟṟāp pēraṉ piṉavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>Pitiable they are,</l>
          <l>those red-mouthed green parakeets—</l>
          <l rend="space">though they see the long [stretches of] fields</l>
          <l>with green-stalked millet stubble</l>
          <l>plucked by the hill-dwellers,</l>
          <l rend="space">they do not understand to leave,</l>
          <l>because of their great love [for millet fields].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
